No

### Description

This won't work:

```
@if(trackBy(); as trackBySignal) {
  @for(item of data; track item[trackBySignal]) {
    <p>
    #{{ item.id }} &mdash; {{ item.name }}
    </p>
  }
}
```

This will work:

```
@for(item of data; track item[trackByNonSignal]) {
  <p>
  #{{ item.id }} &mdash; {{ item.name }}
  </p>
}
```

### Please provide a link to a minimal reproduction of the bug

https://stackblitz.com/edit/stackblitz-starters-dxjcrp?file=src%2Fmain.ts

### Please provide the exception or error you saw

```true
Cannot access 'trackBySignal' inside of a track expression. Only 'item', '$index' and properties on the containing component are available to this expression.
```


